326
00:28:29,059 --> 00:28:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] Velik broj njih.

327
00:28:32,059 --> 00:28:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] I tu dolazimo do toga

328
00:28:38,059 --> 00:28:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] da je istina vrlo, vrlo duboka.

329
00:28:43,059 --> 00:28:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] ali da se za njom

330
00:28:45,059 --> 00:28:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] isplati traga, da se za nju isprati boriti.

331
00:28:54,059 --> 00:28:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] pitao sam Don Tomu, a gdje je ta istina?

332
00:29:00,059 --> 00:29:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] pokazao mi je na križ.

333
00:29:06,059 --> 00:29:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] ondje je istina.

334
00:29:08,059 --> 00:29:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] Završit ću

335
00:29:12,059 --> 00:29:14,059
[SPEAKER_00] sa njegovim

336
00:29:14,059 --> 00:29:18,059
[SPEAKER_00] mladom isničkim vjeslom

337
00:29:18,059 --> 00:29:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] iz Sirahove knjige.

338
00:29:23,059 --> 00:29:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] ondje piše

339
00:29:25,059 --> 00:29:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] do smrti se bori za istinu

340
